OL,3,C'There's so much business': Hopes
OL,4,Ceconomic links with China will grow
OL,6,FGrowing economic ties between the and
OL,7,FAsia present major opportunities,
OL,8,Faccording to business leaders.
OL,10,FMany of the world's largest emerging
OL,11,Fmarkets are in the region, as well as
OL,12,Fa sizeable percentage of the global
OL,13,Fpopulation.
OL,15,FThe Channel Islands are already well-
OL,16,Fpositioned as a number of world-
OL,17,Fleading financial and legal firms that
OL,18,Fhave offices in and also have several
OL,19,Facross the continent.
