OL,3,C'There's so much business': Hopes
OL,4,Ceconomic links with China will grow
OL,6,FJersey, in particular, has had a
OL,7,Fprosperous relationship with the
OL,8,Fregion for several years - a Jersey
OL,9,FFinance report published in November
OL,10,F2021 found the money flowing through
OL,11,Fthe island supported nearly two and
OL,12,Fhalf million jobs in Asia between 2017
OL,13,Fand 2020.
OL,15,FIn comparison, the economic activity
OL,16,Fon the island supported less than a
OL,17,Fmillion jobs in the UK during the same
OL,18,Fperiod.
