OL,3,C'There's so much business': Hopes
OL,4,Ceconomic links with China will grow
OL,6,FMore specifically, business leaders
OL,7,Fsay there are growing opportunities
OL,8,Ffor the Channel Islands in and Hong
OL,9,FKong, which is a Chinese Special
OL,10,FAdministrative Region (SAR).
OL,12,FLast year, Jersey-based companies
OL,13,Flisted on the Hong Kong Stock Exchange
OL,14,Fwere valued at more than #4.5 billion.
OL,16,FSuch is the importance of the region,
OL,17,FJersey Finance now has offices in both
OL,18,FHong Kong and Shanghai.
