OL,3,C'There's so much business': Hopes
OL,4,Ceconomic links with China will grow
OL,6,FMaria McDermott, who represents the
OL,7,Forganisation in China, also says
OL,8,Frecent changes to global regulations
OL,9,Fhave "levelled up the playing field"
OL,10,Ffor jurisdictions like Jersey.
OL,12,FHer job involves boosting the island's
OL,13,Fprofile in the region: "We are working
OL,14,Fhard to raise the brand profile and
OL,15,Feducate people on Jersey as a
OL,16,Fjurisdiction. China is a massive
OL,17,Fmarket. There's so much business.
OL,18,FThere's enough for everybody."
