OL,3,C'There's so much business': Hopes
OL,4,Ceconomic links with China will grow
OL,6,FOne way to further improve the Channel
OL,7,FIslands' economic relationship with
OL,8,FAsia, and especially China, is to get
OL,9,Fa better grasp of the language and
OL,10,Fculture, according to a legal expert.
OL,12,FMarcus Leese is Chair of the Guernsey
OL,13,FBar and has spent many years working
OL,14,Fand travelling in Hong Kong and
OL,15,Fmainland China - during this time, he
OL,16,Fhas seen how helpful even a basic
OL,17,Funderstanding of words or traditions
OL,18,Fcan be.
