OL,3,C'There's so much business': Hopes
OL,4,Ceconomic links with China will grow
OL,6,FHe says: "The reputation of Guernsey
OL,7,Fand Jersey has developed hugely and
OL,8,Fthat's in large part because of
OL,9,Fgreater familiarity with the culture
OL,10,Fand language of the region. It's
OL,11,Fsomething our clients find very, very
OL,12,Fvaluable."
OL,14,FLearning Mandarin is a challenge
OL,15,Falready on the radar for a number of
OL,16,Fislanders, with some attending a
OL,17,Flanguage school in St Helier which
OL,18,Fruns classes for students from pre-
OL,19,Fschool age right up to adulthood.
