OL,3,C'There's so much business': Hopes
OL,4,Ceconomic links with China will grow
OL,6,FWith China undoubtedly set to remain
OL,7,Fan economic and cultural superpower,
OL,8,Fparents who have enrolled their
OL,9,Fchildren for language tuition from a
OL,10,Fyoung age believe it could give them
OL,11,Fan advantage in the future.
OL,13,FOne parent, Daian Sumner, says: "It's
OL,14,Fonly going to grow and that's the
OL,15,Fdirection of travel, so why wouldn't
OL,16,Fyou want to invest in your child so
OL,17,Fthey had a piece of that future?"
