OL,3,C'There's so much business': Hopes
OL,4,Ceconomic links with China will grow
OL,6,FAnother parent, Suzanne Howe, adds:
OL,7,F"To learn something at this young age
OL,8,Fand to see all the different cultures
OL,9,Fand why people do different things in
OL,10,Fdifferent ways is a really good skill
OL,11,Ffor them to have."
OL,13,FTensions persist between the West and
OL,14,FChina due to alleged human rights
OL,15,Fabuses being carried out in the
OL,16,Fcountry.
