OL,3,C'There's so much business': Hopes
OL,4,Ceconomic links with China will grow
OL,6,FNevertheless, trade between it and the
OL,7,FUK remain strong, and while that
OL,8,Fcontinues, politicians in the Channel
OL,9,FIslands say they welcome improved
OL,10,Feconomic ties with China.
OL,12,FJersey's Minister for Sustainable
OL,13,FEconomic Development, Deputy Kirsten
OL,14,FMorel, says: "As long as the UK is
OL,15,Fhappy with the UK doing business with
OL,16,FChina, then that's the stance that
OL,17,FJersey is likely to have, and it's the
OL,18,Fsame for most jurisdictions."
