OL,3,C'There's so much business': Hopes
OL,4,Ceconomic links with China will grow
OL,6,FHowever, he adds representatives from
OL,7,Fthe island voice their concerns about
OL,8,Falleged human rights abuses when they
OL,9,Fvisit countries where that could be an
OL,10,Fissue.
OL,12,FDeputy Morel explains: "I do know that
OL,13,Fwhen ministers have been on missions
OL,14,Fto other jurisdictions where people
OL,15,Fbelieve there are human rights issues,
OL,16,Fministers do tell me when they have
OL,17,Fcome back that they have spoken to the
OL,18,Fleaders in those places about the
OL,19,Fhuman rights issues."
